OL,3,C78-year-old man arrested after James
OL,4,CBulger's grave vandalised
OL,6,FThe grave of murdered toddler James
OL,7,FBulger has been vandalised for the
OL,8,Fsecond time in six weeks.
OL,10,FOfficers from Merseyside Police were
OL,11,Fcalled to Kirkdale Cemetery in
OL,12,FLiverpool on Friday afternoon, 10
OL,13,FApril, after reports of damage to the
OL,14,Fgrave.
OL,16,FJames was two-years-old when he was
OL,17,Fabducted from shopping centre in
OL,18,FBootle and murdered by 10-year-old
OL,19,Fboys Robert Thompson and Jon Venables
OL,20,Fin 1993.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
