OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776066987
OL,3,C78-year-old man arrested after James
OL,4,CBulger's grave vandalised
OL,6,FA 78-year-old man from Kirkby was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of criminal
OL,8,Fdamage and theft and is being
OL,9,Fquestioned by police.
OL,11,FDetective Sergeant Michelle Devereux
OL,12,Fsaid: "A man will now be questioned,
OL,13,Fand we will continue to update and
OL,14,Fsupport James's family as the
OL,15,Finvestigation progresses.
OL,17,F"I would encourage anyone with
OL,18,Finformation to come forward directly
OL,19,Fto police as soon as possible, in any
OL,20,Fof the following ways."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
