PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776066987
OL,3,C78-year-old man arrested after James
OL,4,CBulger's grave vandalised
OL,6,FThe grave was previously damaged in
OL,7,FFebruary when the two cherub statues
OL,8,Fwere smashed.
OL,10,FSpeaking after the first instance of
OL,11,Fvandalism, James' mother Denise Fergus
OL,12,Fsaid she was "devastated" after the
OL,13,F"truly shocking" act of vandalism.
OL,15,FIt is not known whether the two
OL,16,Finstances are connected.
OL,18,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,19,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,20,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,21,Four region.
